# Part 7: Complete Model Parameter Count

| Component | Parameters | Calculation |
|---|---|---|
| PatchEmbed Conv2d | 6,272 | $(3 \times 4 \times 4 + 1) \times 128 = 49 \times 128$ (with bias) |
| CLS token | 128 | $1 \times 128$ |
| Positional embedding | 8,320 | $65 \times 128$ |
| **Per DiffHead** | **20,481** | $4 \times (128 \times 32) + (128 \times 32) + 1$ |
| **Per MultiHeadAttn** | **98,180** | $4 \times 20481 + 128 \times 128 + 128$ |
| **Per FFN** | **131,584** | $128 \times 512 + 512 + 512 \times 128 + 128$ |
| **Per LayerNorm** | **256** | $128 + 128$ (scale + shift) |
| **Per LNBlock** | **230,276** | MHA + FFN + 2×LN |
| **6 Blocks Total** | **1,381,656** | $6 \times 230276$ |
| Final LN | 256 | |
| Classification head | 1,290 | $128 \times 10 + 10$ |
| **Grand Total** | **~1.4M** | All of the above |

For comparison, a standard ViT with the same architecture (single Q/K per head) would have ~1.2M parameters. The differential mechanism adds ~17% more parameters due to the doubled Q/K projections.

